    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, you have to see this beauty in person\u2014it looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and there isn't a single scratch or blemish anywhere. It drives like an absolute dream and still has that new-car smell. I'm really sad to let it go, but I know it's going to make someone very happy. Come swing by and take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
