    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This vehicle is a pristine, 'time capsule' example that has been maintained to the most exacting standards. The exterior is finished in a deep, lustrous paint that has been professionally treated with a multi-stage ceramic coating, ensuring a mirror-like reflection free of swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections. The interior remains in showroom condition; the high-grade leather upholstery shows absolutely no bolster wear or creasing, and the cabin still retains its original new-car scent. Every electronic component, from the premium sound system to the driver-assist features, operates with factory precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been serviced exclusively at the dealership on a strictly time-based schedule rather than mileage. It has been stored in a climate-controlled garage under a soft cover and has never been driven in inclement weather. Included with the sale are all original keys, the factory window sticker, and a comprehensive binder of every service record since new. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the showroom floor.",
      "price": 44800.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
